      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rav Yosef I, third-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"1764\" data-full-name=\"Rav Yosef I\" data-name-he=\"רב יוסף בר חייא\">רַב יוֹסֵף</span>: אַמַּאי סָמְכַתְּ – אַהַאי שְׁטָרָא; הַאי",
      "segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "שְׁטָרָא חַסְפָּא בְּעָלְמָא הוּא. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"2\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>הַהוּא דְּאָמַר",
