      "text": "<span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rav Dimi bar Abba I, third and fourth-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"343\" data-full-name=\"Rav Dimi bar Abba I\" data-name-he=\"רב אידי בר אבין\" data-crossline-group=\"name-ref-crossline-4450\">אָבִין</span>: הִלְכְתָא כְּווֹתֵיהּ <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rabba bar Naḥmani, third-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"2581\" data-full-name=\"Rabba bar Naḥmani\" data-name-he=\"רבה בר נחמני\">דְּרַבָּה</span> בְּאַרְעָא, וְהִלְכְתָא",
